# Files and directories that should be included in the public repository
# One file/directory per line
# Lines starting with # are comments

# Documentation
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE
MULTI_PROJECT_CONFIG.md

# Configuration
.gitignore
package.json
package-lock.json

# Source code
jaxon-optimizely-dxp-mcp.js
lib/
