# NEVER include these files in public repo:
# - CLAUDE.md (internal development notes)
# - MCP_TEST_PLAN.md (internal testing)
# - .env* files (credentials)
# - test-* files (test scripts and data)
# - scripts/check-secrets.sh (security tools)
# - .gitleaks.toml (security config)
# - *.bacpac, *.nupkg, *.zip (packages)